cat << EOF
Fireflies is an OpenGL screensaver for Linux (using xscreensaver) and
Windows. It also works as a standalone program, which allows you to move
and rotate the camera. Swarms of bugs fly around the screen leaving colorful
translucent trails that get blown around by the wind.
